graph TD
    subgraph Client Layer
        UI[React Webclient]
    end

    subgraph Core Layer
        CoreServer[Core Server Node.js]
        RedisCache[(Redis Cache)]
        Postgres[(PostgreSQL)]
    end

    subgraph Tracking Service
        TrackServer[Tracking Service]
    end

    subgraph AI Layer
        Analyzer[Python Analyzer]
    end

    subgraph Infrastructure
        RMQ{{RabbitMQ}}
        Internet((Internet))
    end

    UI -->|1. Search Stock 'TSLA'| CoreServer
    CoreServer -->|2. Generate ScanJobId| CoreServer
    CoreServer -->|3. Check Cache| RedisCache
    CoreServer -->|4. If Cache Miss - HTTP POST| TrackServer
    TrackServer -->|5. Scrape News| Internet
    TrackServer -->|6. Return Expected Article Count| CoreServer
    TrackServer -->|7. Publish Tasks w/ ScanJobId| RMQ
    RMQ -->|8. Consume Tasks| Analyzer
    Analyzer -->|9. Process & Publish Results| RMQ
    RMQ -->|10. Deliver Analyzed Articles| CoreServer
    CoreServer -->|11. Save History & Live Score| Postgres
    CoreServer -->|12. Update Cache| RedisCache
    
    %% Stream & Aggregate Logic
    CoreServer -->|13. Aggregate Articles PER JOB| CoreServer
    CoreServer -.->|14. Job_TSLA Finished - Stream ndJSON Row| UI
    CoreServer -.->|15. All Jobs Finished - Stream Terminal Message & Close| UI
